These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, gospel, hip-hop, trance, indie, disco
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, february, march, december, may, november, january
 1. the fan d&b is between the fan hip-hop and the fan disco##2
 2. the fan house is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the fan trance is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan disco##1
 9. the fan trance is on the left of the fan indie##1
10. the fan trance is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the fan indie is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | d&b | disco | house    | gospel | trance   | indie    |
| Birthday         | november  | february   | december | september | march   | january | may |

