.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, march, august, july, december, may, january
7 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, turtle, goldfish, cat, mouse, frog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in may and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday          | december | august | may | march | january | april      | july  |
| Pet   | mouse | goldfish  | frog     | turtle     | cat  | ferret | dog |

