.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
City: colone, paris, rome, london, venice, nizza, san-francisco
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, baccarat, aristoff, blend, havana, fonseca, dunhill
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the havana-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to london is the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the person traveling to london##2
 9. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| City   | san-francisco | venice | colone | paris   | london | rome | nizza |
| Cigar           | havana | fonseca     | baccarat     | aristoff | blend   | davidoff   | dunhill    |

