.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, billiard, whist, monopoly, backgammon, domino
House: tower, palace, futuristic, colonial, victorian, cottage, gothic-revival
1. the colonial house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is the person playing snooker##1
3. the tower house is between the person playing domino and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the victorian house##1
5. the tower house is in the middle##1
6. the cottage house is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1
8. the palace house is the person playing whist##1
9. the person playing monopoly is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Game   | whist      | monopoly | mah-jongg | billiard | domino      | snooker      | backgammon |
| House     | palace | cottage | gothic-revival       | tower | futuristic | victorian | colonial |

