 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's birthday is in october##2
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
